OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FEngland international Missy Bo Kearns
OL,8,Fspeaks for the first time about her
OL,9,Fmiscarriage, telling Stacey Foster
OL,10,Fthat baby loss is 'a different type of
OL,11,Fgrief' and how sepsis led to 'days of
OL,12,Fhell in hospital' with her partner
OL,13,FLiam Walsh
OL,15,FWhen I first met Missy Bo Kearns, we'd
OL,16,Fbeen invited to Aston Villa to film
OL,17,Fher at the club following her
OL,18,Fpregnancy announcement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FThe 24-year-old midfielder was excited
OL,8,Fat the idea of becoming the first
OL,9,FEngland international in recent years
OL,10,Fto give birth and return to
OL,11,Finternational football. She hoped to
OL,12,Fget back into the Lionesses squad in
OL,13,Ftime for next year's World Cup in
OL,14,FBrazil.
OL,16,FBefore we were able to do the
OL,17,Finterview, Missy was taken to the
OL,18,Fhospital. She'd started to feel unwell.
OL,20,FWe were shocked and really concerned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FI remember seeing Missy as she left
OL,8,FVilla's training ground, Bodymoor
OL,9,FHeath, with her partner Liam Walsh, a
OL,10,Fmidfielder at Luton Town.
OL,12,FWe exchanged reassuring smiles, and I
OL,13,Fsaid I'd see her soon, and I genuinely
OL,14,Fthought we would. We both did.
OL,16,FI found out, like everyone else, that
OL,17,FMissy and Liam had lost their baby
OL,18,Fwhen she announced it on Instagram a
OL,19,Ffew weeks later. They asked for
OL,20,Fprivacy and time to heal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FFive weeks after that first visit, we
OL,8,Fwere invited to Aston Villa's training.
OL,10,FMissy is back at work, and we meet
OL,11,Fagain, under another cloudless Spring
OL,12,Fsky. But she is here to tell a
OL,13,Fdifferent story.
OL,15,FMissy Bo Kearns tells how her life
OL,16,F'changed, just like that' as she
OL,17,Flearnt in hospital that she had
OL,18,Fdeveloped sepsis and lost her baby
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FMissy Bo is the heart and soul of
OL,8,FAston Villa. Their number seven is a
OL,9,Fjoker; she's full of mischief and has
OL,10,Fa smile that radiates around the
OL,11,Fbuilding.
OL,13,FIt's only her third day back. She is
OL,14,Fbeing monitored closely during her
OL,15,Frecovery from a "septic miscarriage".
OL,26,@wD@QOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FWhen we start the interview, it's
OL,8,Fobvious that Missy is ready to tell
OL,9,Fher story. After all, her team had
OL,10,Fbeen in touch to say she wanted to
OL,11,Fspeak to us, and as we started, her
OL,12,Ffeelings spilt out.
OL,14,FShe takes me back to that day in
OL,15,FMarch, when she got "the shivers", and
OL,16,Fthe club doctor, Jodie Blackadder-
OL,17,FWeinstein, advised her to call Liam
OL,18,Fstraight away, and go to the hospital.
OL,26,@wD@UOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"It was one of the biggest shocks of
OL,8,Fmy life. I thought it was just like a
OL,9,Fpregnancy symptom, and the doctor came
OL,10,Fin and checked my temperature...",
OL,11,FMissy says.
OL,13,F"I was 42 degrees, but I was shaking.
OL,14,FAnd the doctor said to me, 'Where's
OL,15,FLiam?' And I was like, 'I'm not going
OL,16,Fback to the hospital. I literally went
OL,17,Fa few days ago. Everything's fine.
OL,18,FThey told me everything's fine.' And
OL,19,Fshe said, 'Ring Liam.' And I was like,
OL,20,F'He's had a night game. He's in bed
OL,21,Fstill.'"
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@aO]uD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"But I rang him, and he came. We went
OL,8,Fto the hospital, and that's when we
OL,9,Ffound out that straight away, we had
OL,10,Flost the baby and that I'd got sepsis."
OL,12,F"So, it was difficult, like it was a
OL,13,Fshock, because I'd literally been
OL,14,Fdoing Pilates and gym an hour before,
OL,15,Fand my whole life just changed like
OL,16,Fthat."
OL,18,FAnyone who has experience of pregnancy
OL,19,Floss will instantly relate to what
OL,20,FMissy Bo says.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@gO]tD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"Is there something I've done? Is
OL,8,Fthere something I didn't? But it's
OL,9,Fnot. And I hope people out there
OL,10,Fwho've been through it know that it's
OL,11,Fwhat's meant to be, will be, and it
OL,12,Fhappens for a reason, even though it's
OL,13,Fso hard to come to terms with that;
OL,14,Fthere's nothing that you can do to
OL,15,Fstop it or prevent it.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"So that's one message that I'd like
OL,8,Fto get out there, because I can tell
OL,9,Fyou now a lot of people have probably
OL,10,Fhad thoughts that I've had, or what my
OL,11,Fpartner might have had, like, did we
OL,12,Fnot check something, or were we not
OL,13,Fclear on something?
OL,15,F"But there's literally nothing you can
OL,16,Fdo. And other than trying your best to
OL,17,Fbelieve that everything happens for a
OL,18,Freason, and to be positive. And
OL,19,Fthere's always a time, next time.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"And I think that's what's the hardest
OL,8,Fthing, because you overthink. Well, I
OL,9,Fpersonally overthink a lot, and I
OL,10,Fthink a lot of women definitely do."
OL,12,FIn a message to others who have been
OL,13,Fthrough baby loss, Kearns urges them
OL,14,Fnot to blame themselves for something
OL,15,Fthey have no control over
OL,17,FMissy Bo says the medical team at
OL,18,FVilla saved her life, but all she
OL,19,Fcould think about was losing her child.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"We had to go through like, three,
OL,8,Ffour days of hell in hospital, the two
OL,9,Fof us, up in Birmingham. I don't think
OL,10,Fwe realised how much we went through
OL,11,Funtil now, when you sit back.
OL,13,F"I'm so thankful for the doctors here
OL,14,Fat Villa, because if I was at home
OL,15,Fthat day, and I probably would have
OL,16,Frung, my mum saying, 'Oh, I feel a bit
OL,17,Flike flu-ish symptoms', everyone would
OL,18,Fjust say, 'Have a sleep' or whatnot.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"And Jodie made me go to the hospital,
OL,8,Fand I was not wanting to go, because
OL,9,Fthere's nothing worse than obviously
OL,10,Fgoing to a hospital.
OL,12,F"But they probably saved my life
OL,13,Fbecause I had sepsis, and while having
OL,14,Fthat, I wasn't even thinking about the
OL,15,Fsepsis. It was 'I've lost my child'."
OL,26,@wD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FShe cannot say enough times how
OL,8,Fgrateful she is for the support she
OL,9,Fhas had. From both her home club,
OL,10,FAston Villa, England, her partner's
OL,11,Fclub, Luton Town, their team-mates,
OL,12,Ftheir families, but also from
OL,13,Fstrangers.
OL,15,FMissy also says she is proud of Liam,
OL,16,Fwho, weeks after the miscarriage,
OL,17,Flifted the Vertu Trophy at Wembley
OL,18,Fwith Luton Town.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FThe "perks" of football are not lost
OL,8,Fon her. She knows she has more support
OL,9,Fthan many and is grateful for it, but
OL,10,Fshe hopes that by opening the
OL,11,Fconversation, she can offer something
OL,12,Fto others going through the same
OL,13,Fexperience.
OL,15,F"You actually feel like you're the
OL,16,Fonly person it's ever happened to. But
OL,17,Freally, it's so common, and that's why
OL,18,FI think it's important that the
OL,19,Fmessage is out there and don't feel
OL,20,Falone and stuff, because it's happened
OL,21,Fto so many people."
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@KO]wD@AOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"I think people might not realise how
OL,8,Fmuch of a toll it actually has on
OL,9,Fsomeone. I think obviously everyone
OL,10,Fknows how hard it must be to lose a
OL,11,Fchild, but obviously, because of the
OL,12,Fhighs of finding out you're pregnant,
OL,13,Fand the stress of being pregnant, and
OL,14,Flike, the worries of getting past the
OL,15,F12 week mark, and like, it's so
OL,16,Fstressful, even though it's so
OL,17,Fexciting.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"I think to then have that crash, and
OL,8,Fthen suddenly you're not pregnant, and
OL,9,Fyour hormones change, your symptoms
OL,10,Fstart to go, like overnight. I think
OL,11,Fit's a different type of grief. It's
OL,12,Fnot (something) that I've ever
OL,13,Fexperienced before..."
OL,15,F"I just think everyone obviously
OL,16,Fgrieves differently... I think a lot
OL,17,Fof people, if someone's going through
OL,18,Fa miscarriage, they don't know.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@EpmtD@OpnuD@VO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"People don't tell people that they've
OL,8,Fbeen through it. They suffer in
OL,9,Fsilence. And I just hope that people
OL,10,Fmay not suffer in silence now, knowing
OL,11,Fthat, like I'm here, if anyone wants
OL,12,Fto speak, there are charities like
OL,13,FTommy's, so many other charities that,
OL,14,Fif anyone needs them, have reached out
OL,15,Fto me for support."
OL,17,FKearns tells of her road to recovery,
OL,18,Fboth physical and emotional, and her
OL,19,Fhopes for next year's World Cup
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FAnd she is honest about how losing the
OL,8,Fbaby has impacted her mentally.
OL,10,F"Now it's when it starts to feel real,
OL,11,Fwhen you've got to start organising
OL,12,Fthings, then when you realise the
OL,13,Fplans that you had, like coming up
OL,14,Faren't the same plans no more.
OL,16,F"This is when it starts to hit you.
OL,17,FAnd I think I'd say the past week or
OL,18,Fso is where it's hit me. Most of them,
OL,19,FI've been struggling like a lot more
OL,20,Fthan the first week or so, I'd say.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
