OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"I think I've been trying to keep
OL,8,Fmyself busy. I wouldn't say I'm fully
OL,9,Fcoping. Yeah, there are days like
OL,10,Ftoday where I feel good. I've been in
OL,11,Fand around the (Aston Villa) girls and
OL,12,Fstuff.
OL,14,F"I've done my bike, I've done my
OL,15,Ftesting, like, ready to get back onto
OL,16,Fit. But yesterday, I was upset all day
OL,17,Fbecause I got some news that the
OL,18,Fthings we have to sort and it just
OL,19,Fcomes and goes in waves.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@PpmsD@\pnvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30621
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"And I think keeping myself busy, I
OL,8,Fthink going to watch Liam's games, has
OL,9,Fhelped.
OL,11,F"But also, I've been kind of trying to
OL,12,Fgo through it a bit isolated, than
OL,13,Fhaving time to myself and to
OL,14,Fourselves, like not being around
OL,15,Fpeople.
OL,17,F"That's helped me a lot. I get a bit
OL,18,Fanxious being around people in case
OL,19,Fthey asked me how I am and stuff,
OL,20,Fbecause I don't want to talk about it
OL,21,Fall the time.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30622
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"But sometimes I'm in a mood where I
OL,8,Fwant to talk about it. I want to let
OL,9,Fmy emotions out and what's on my chest
OL,10,Fand stuff. So, it just depends. I
OL,11,Fwouldn't say I've got a full coping
OL,12,Fmechanism.
OL,14,F"I'm hoping now that I'm well enough
OL,15,Fto come back into football, getting
OL,16,Fback fit and training, being around my
OL,17,Ffriends."
OL,19,FMissy turned 25 while navigating this
OL,20,Fmost difficult time in her life and
OL,21,Ffootball career.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/29
