OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FShe moved to Birmingham in 2024 after
OL,8,Fmaking more than 100 appearances in
OL,9,Fthe Women's Super League for Liverpool.
OL,11,FIn the summer of 2025, Missy made her
OL,12,FEngland senior debut in the Lionesses'
OL,13,FNations League tie away to Spain. Her
OL,14,Ffirst start for England came six
OL,15,Fmonths later in a friendly against
OL,16,FGhana.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30624
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FMissy says she is in no rush to return
OL,8,Fto competitive football, especially
OL,9,Fthis close to the end of the season.
OL,10,FShe wants to be mentally and
OL,11,Fphysically ready.
OL,13,FShe mentions a sevens-tournament in
OL,14,Fthe summer, but says pre-season is her
OL,15,Ffocus for now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G24/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30625
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,FWhat is clear, though, is that,
OL,8,Fdespite everything that has changed in
OL,9,Fonly a few weeks, her ambitions have
OL,10,Fstayed the same. She wants to play for
OL,11,FEngland at next summer's World Cup in
OL,12,FBrazil.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G25/29
