OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"I've got to do a return-to-play
OL,8,Fprotocol. So, it's been like a big,
OL,9,Ffull process, because when I'm
OL,10,Finjured, I hate doing rehab and stuff
OL,11,Fas it is, but I'm not actually
OL,12,Finjured, but I need to gradually build
OL,13,Fmy body back up.
OL,15,F"I do know that being back in
OL,16,Ffootball, it's my happy place, and I'm
OL,17,Fhere now, and I'm excited to be here
OL,18,Fand like, keep trying to build and
OL,19,Fbuild and get myself right ready for
OL,20,Fnext season.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
