OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30627
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"I want to come back in pre-season and
OL,8,Fbe back to the Missy Bo everyone knows
OL,9,Fwho's smiling, happy, winding people
OL,10,Fup non-stop.
OL,12,F"And I think it's a big year next
OL,13,Fyear, and my plan while I was pregnant
OL,14,Fwas to make the World Cup squad, and
OL,15,Fthat's not changed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/29
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30628
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777277174
OL,3,CLioness Kearns says Villa doctor
OL,4,C'probably saved my life' after
OL,5,Cmiscarriage
OL,7,F"So, the next few months is getting
OL,8,Fmyself, physically, mentally strong,
OL,9,Fready for a big season, and to try and
OL,10,Fmake the World Cup squad and also have
OL,11,Fa positive full season for villa, like
OL,12,FI'm just excited.
OL,14,F"I've realised, like there's more to
OL,15,Flife than football, but now I'm going
OL,16,Fto enjoy every minute of football like
OL,17,Fit's my last because it could have
OL,18,Fbeen."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
